{"title":"Bear Grylls and Brompton Run Wild with New Collaboration","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bear-grylls-brompton-folding-bike-collaboration/","date":1695647946000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor.jpg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore bear carries bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor.jpg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Bear-Grylls-Brompton-Bikerumor-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>When British adventurer Edward Michael “Bear” Grylls climbed to the top of Mount Everest, he was 23 years old, making him among the youngest ever to do so. Since then, he’s been a famous adventure guy doing all sorts of adventure-y types of things, like his most recent adventure, a <a href=\"https://us.brompton.com/p/976/us-brompton-x-bear-grylls-c-line-explore?xnpe_tifc=buUubunZbIzphI1jhFP.bMpsafeWaeiWhFW-bf46nkPWRdUZEfJvVN8.adJSbIzp4Dnjx.Q.bIHXbDnjhnTT&amp;utm_source=exponea&amp;utm_campaign=Email_Global_Brompton%20x%20BG%20Launch_Sept%2023&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=en_us\" target=\"_blank\">bike collaboration</a> with the UK <a href=\"https://us.brompton.com/\" target=\"_blank\">folding bike masters</a>, Brompton.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"687\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376-800x687.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore walking on the beach\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376-800x687.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376-297x255.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376-120x103.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376-768x660.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-walking-on-the-beach-e1695316467376.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore on beach folded\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-on-beach-folded.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Brompton says that the Bear Grylls C Line Explore is spec’d for flexibility with six speeds and a Moss Green &amp; Mushroom Gray colorway that is reminiscent of the natural tones found in British woodland expeditions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with other Brompton models, the Bear Grylls C Line Explore “folds down in 20 seconds”. Having a bike that folds down to a locked, compact unit, will aid in any adventure where space is limited.  </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bear Grylls C Line Explore</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"418\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff-800x418.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore against the cliff\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff-800x418.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff-297x155.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff-768x401.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-against-the-cliff.jpeg 1180w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Brompton</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bear obviously likes adventures. According to Brompton, this collaboration will help anyone seek their own adventures and explore new possibilities. The Bear Grylls C Line Explore is built with a focus on versatility and comfort. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore studio\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore studio hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-hero.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When your adventure calls for supplies and sundries, the C Line Explore is ready. It comes equipped with <a href=\"https://us.brompton.com/p/972/brompton-x-bear-grylls-waterproof-backpack?xnpe_tifc=buUubunZbIzphI1jhFP.bMpsafeWaeiWhFW-bf46nkPWRdUZEfJvVN8.adJSbIzp4Dnjx.Q.bIHXbDnjhnTT&amp;utm_source=exponea&amp;utm_campaign=Email_Global_Brompton%20x%20BG%20Launch_Sept%2023&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=en_us\" target=\"_blank\">matching luggage</a>. The waterproof backpack and essentials pouch are ready for anything from your daily commute to a planned exploration. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"539\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo-800x539.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore bear logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo-800x539.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo-297x200.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo-120x81.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo-768x517.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-bear-logo.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore front mounting block\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-front-mounting-block.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>The Brompton Front Carrier Black</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They easily attach and detach from the bike in seconds. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Brompton says it’s easy to unleash your Wanderlust and push new horizons with the Bear Grylls C Line Explore.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bear Grylls C Line Explore Features and Retail</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $2500</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Hand-brazed steel frame</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Waterproof backpack and pouch included</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Two-tone wheelset – silver and black rims</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fenders</li>\n\n\n\n<li>6-speed drivetrain</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Special Edition serial plate</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Brooks Cambium C17 all-weather saddle</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"539\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame-800x539.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore studio rear frame\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame-800x539.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame-297x200.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame-120x81.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame-768x517.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-rear-frame.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"539\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding-800x539.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore adventure orange branding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding-800x539.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding-297x200.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding-120x81.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding-768x517.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-adventure-orange-branding.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore studio partial fold\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-partial-fold.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827-800x381.jpeg\" alt=\"Brompton x Bear Grylls C Line Explore studio folded with luggage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827-800x381.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827-297x142.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827-120x57.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827-768x366.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Brompton-x-Bear-Grylls-C-Line-Explore-studio-folded-with-luggage-e1695316556827.jpeg 1276w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Specs </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the Brompton website:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Frame material: Steel<br />– Front frame: Precision drawn heat-treated steel tubing with hand brazing and selected auto-brazed joints in Moss Green<br />– Rear frame: Hand-brazed cold-formed micro-alloy steel tubing in Mushroom Gray</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork: Handbuilt steel brazed fork in Mushroom Gray</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Saddle: Brooks Cambium C17</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pedals: Brompton Folding left-hand and non-folding right-hand pedals</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bottom bracket: Square taper</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Front-wheel: Double-wall rim, 28 spokes laced to a Brompton front hub</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rear-wheel: Brompton 6-speed Rear Wheel​</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Grips: Lock-on soft compound</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Drivetrain: Brompton Wide-range 6-speed drivetrain (2 x 3 speed), 300% range</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Headset: Brompton headset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Derailleur: Brompton Chain Pusher</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shifters: Brompton 2 and 3-speed Trigger shifters</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To see more details or check out the other Bompton options, hit the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://us.brompton.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Brompton.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bear-grylls-brompton-folding-bike-collaboration/\">Bear Grylls and Brompton Run Wild with New Collaboration</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"486970998b8d15c3699d743493ddc9c452c3110e6611a8bfba5e66352a374f09","category":"Cycling"}